    • Constructor Detail

      • Code

        public Code(java.lang.String key,
            java.lang.String value)
        This class represents a barcode or a QR code (created using the data of the key) for a template. All the options can be set with the setter functions.
        Parameters:
        key - Key_type, e.g. "barcode_type" if the key used is "barcode". This field contains the type of barcode required. The options can be found on: http://www.apexofficeprint.com/docs/#615-barcode-qrcode-tags
        value - Data to create the code from.

      • getQrErrorCorrectionLevel

        public java.lang.String getQrErrorCorrectionLevel()
        Only for QR codes.
        Returns:
        Level at which the QR code should be recoverable. The options are: "L" (up to 7% damage) "M" (up to 15% damage) "Q" (up to 25% damage) "H" (up to 30% damage)

      • setQrErrorCorrectionLevel
